		{"id":"c4d37d60ca8b95f7","type":"text","text":"- Competion is for Loseres\n- Competition is War\n- War is costly business\n- Competition = no profits\n- All competition is Rivalrous and mimetic\n- Pick your Battles\n- Wars not worth Fighting\n- Rivalry is distracting, make you mimetic\n- If you cant beat them join them\n- Monopoly is the opposite of competition\n- Monopoly is the Condition for business","x":284,"y":-54,"width":250,"height":479},
		{"id":"2fc795bc9228b8f3","type":"text","text":"[[Philanthropic]]","x":284,"y":560,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"4aff424069947d80","type":"text","text":"Open sourcing, social entreprunuriship is doing what is percived to be socially good,and what is conde sociall good can only be convention hence no progress, just copying.\n\nCopying leads to mimesis -> mimetic rivalry -> race to the bottom.","x":284,"y":720,"width":250,"height":400},
