		{"id":"88afc5e68b443275","type":"text","text":"# Monopoly Decepton\n- [[Competitive Lies - disguise as interception of small markets|Competitive Lies non monopolist disguise as intercetion of small markets]]\n- [[Craft/Mastercraft/Intelligence/State of the Art/Philosophy/Masculine/Masculine/Masculinity/Masculine Imperative/Monopoly/Monopoly/Monopoly Deception/Monopoly Lies- we are a small fish in big market|Monopoly Lies- we are a small fish in big market]]\n","x":1866,"y":246,"width":599,"height":149},
		{"id":"cde662934f282a95","type":"text","text":"# [[Craft/Tradecraft/Business/Monopoly/4 CHARACTERISTICS OF MONOPOLY/4 CHARACTERISTICS OF MONOPOLY|4 CHARACTERISTICS OF MONOPOLY]]\n- [[Genesis Proprietary Technology|Genesis Proprietary Technology]]\n- [[Craft/Mastercraft/Intelligence/State of the Art/Philosophy/Masculine/Masculine/Masculinity/Masculine Imperative/Monopoly/4 CHARACTERISTICS OF MONOPOLY/Path Dependence- Network Effects|Path Dependence- Network Effects]]\n- [[Craft/Tradecraft/Business/Monopoly/4 CHARACTERISTICS OF MONOPOLY/Scale Dependenc- Economies of Scale|Scale Dependenc- Economies of Scale]]\n- [[Mimetic Foundation - Branding|Mimetic Foundation - Branding]]","x":1866,"y":-8,"width":480,"height":194},
